# API Reference

Base URL: `https://<your-domain>/api`

| Endpoint                | Method | Description                                  |
|-------------------------|--------|----------------------------------------------|
| `/auth/login`           | POST   | User authentication â†’ returns JWT cookie     |
| `/auth/logout`          | POST   | Clears session cookie                        |
| `/quiz/:moduleId`       | POST   | Generate quiz questions for a given module   |
| `/quiz/:quizId/submit`  | POST   | Submit answers, returns score & feedback     |
| `/chat`                 | POST   | SSE chat assistant (streaming responses)     |
| `/analytics/time`       | POST   | Log time-on-task event                       |

## Request / Response Schemas
### `/quiz/:moduleId` request
```json
{ "moduleId": "string", "numQuestions": 5 }
